jobInfo.postDescription:
We are looking for a highly skilled computer programmer who is comfortable with both front and back end programming. Your primary responsibility will be to develop and design front end and back-end architecture, ensuring the responsiveness of applications.

Responsibilities
-----------------
Developing front end website architecture.
Designing user interactions on web pages.
Developing back-end applications.
Ensuring responsiveness of applications.
Seeing through a project from conception to finished product.
Designing and developing APIs.
Meeting both technical and consumer needs.

Skills and qualifications
-------------------------
Degree in computer science
Proficiency with fundamental front-end languages such as HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
Familiarity with JavaScript frameworks such as Angular JS, React, or Vue
Proficiency with server-side Java programing languages.
Familiarity with database technology such as MySQL, Oracle, and MongoDB.
Excellent verbal communication skills.
Good problem-solving skills.
Attention to detail.

brandComInfo.introduce:
方图数据是前Oracle技术大牛创立的数据库类基础软件开发企业，核心技术团队均来自Oracle的数据库、云计算及WebLogic中间件等软件产品的全球核心研发团队。
方图数据和国家电网直属研究院国网智能电网研究院在数据库软件、知识图谱、分布式应用系统等领域结成战略合作伙伴，双方强强联合，优势互补。
方图数据聚焦自研数据库软件，现有图数据库产品已推出，后续将陆续推出时序数据库、文档数据库、关系数据库等产品。
公司处于快速发展期，发展潜力巨大。
扁平化结构，人性化管理。
园区工作环境优美，有多达几十个班车路线到达全市各主要区域。
